<item>
            <title>[SPR-739] Step-by-step tutorial broken with HSQLDB 1.7.2+</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-739</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HSQLDB 1.7.2+ requires even an inprocess database to be explicitly shutdown.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Without doing this, the TestProductManagerDaoJdbc.java unit test fails.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I resolved it by adding a shutdown task and making it the final dependency for the junit task as follows.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;target name=&quot;junit&quot; depends=&quot;build, clearData, loadData, shutdown&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
            description=&quot;Run JUnit Tests&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
       ...&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/target&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;target name=&quot;shutdown&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;echo message=&quot;SHUTDOWN: $&lt;/p&gt;
{db.driver} ${db.url}&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;sql driver=&quot;${db.driver}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
             url=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{db.url}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
             userid=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{db.user}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
             password=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{db.pw}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
             onerror=&quot;continue&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;classpath refid=&quot;master-classpath&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;        SHUTDOWN;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;        &amp;lt;/sql&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/target&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
